      "text": [
        " اَلْوَسْوَسَةِ فِي اَلْخَلْقِ مَا لَمْ يَنْطِقِ اَلْإِنْسَانُ بِشَفَةٍ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.132 - The Prophet (sw) said:\n\"Nine things have been lifted from my community: mistakes, errors, forgetfulness, what they are compelled to do, what they do not know, what they cannot endure, superstitions, envy (if not acted upon), and thoughts of doubt in creation as long as a person does not express them verbally.\""
        ]
      }
